{"tid":1369482,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［不割𥱊］光復元朗，和理勇武！","createTime":"2019-07-26T17:00:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-27T01:36:07.000Z","uid":17244,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"0c35103b68eef5e8b717e051f391335bf8b5dd39","tid":1369482,"uid":17244,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T17:00:16.000Z","msg":"成場運動由6月9為持到今日絕對係靠<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">香港人同行，WE CONNECT！</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n雖然小弟能力有限只能和理非咁入元朗SHOPPING，亦唔太主張喺元朗主動出擊<br />\n但若有鄉黑黎搞我地，請戰士狠狠地自衛！<br />\n<br />\n今日和理非去撐勇武，勇武既去保護和理非！<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">光復香港，時代革命！</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"fc81d3680b98e88cff07f8beca59edcd2e471b5f","tid":1369482,"uid":276208,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T17:00:45.000Z","msg":"借位一用<br />\n<br />\n<strong>請幫推到鄉民見到，希望聽日可以相安無事</strong><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: blue;\">誠懇請鄉民今次真係要<ins>阻止任何可疑人士（包括疑似示威者）入村</ins>，唔係又引起誤會／衝突就唔好啦~~ </span></strong><br />\n<br />\n[投訴懶人包] 反對套丁及冒充原居民 <br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1369127\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1369127</a><br />\n<br />\n<em><span style=\"color: blue;\">齊上齊落，支持五大訴求<br />\n支持圍村去黑，還我平靜鄉郊<br />\n反恐反黑，由投訴撚做起</span></em>"},{"pid":"98eca468e30a8d72a9ed1b8b1e716d835026e448","tid":1369482,"uid":17244,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T17:06:32.000Z","msg":"PUSH&middot;"},{"pid":"494a10d721ad6729c9920c3463c79c6b2ec84f97","tid":1369482,"uid":17244,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T17:08:40.000Z","msg":"光復香港"},{"pid":"bff8b4bcbd20e37b20205b7e05a444f48a2dd4b4","tid":1369482,"uid":280830,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T17:09:33.000Z","msg":"push<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8b6698173771cc195c6b1d96e0c616188c03b39","tid":1369482